PortSystem 1.0
name		lame
version		3.93.1
revision	1
categories	audio
maintainers	jpm@opendarwin.org
description	Lame Ain't an MP3 Encoder
long_description	\
	LAME is an educational tool to be used for learning about MP3 \
	encoding. The goal of the LAME project is to use the open source \
	model to improve the psycho acoustics, noise shaping and speed of \
	MP3. LAME is not for everyone - it is distributed as source code \
	only and requires the ability to use a C compiler.
homepage	http://www.mp3dev.org
platforms	darwin freebsd
master_sites	\
	http://unc.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lame/ \
	http://telia.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lame/ \
	http://easynews.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lame/ \
	http://umn.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lame/ \
	http://twtelecom.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lame/ \
	http://belnet.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lame/ \
	http://switch.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lame/ \
	http://cesnet.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/lame/
